==Description==
The '''Dread Plate''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The Dread Plate has a value of 100 [[Gems|Dark Gems]] {{Gem|Dark}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Acquisition==
Dread Plates can be found in the [[Underground]], traded for with the [[Berry Master|Hoenn Berry Master]], and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

